  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As you hold your hands with thumbs touching and fingers spread, a thin sheet of flames shoots forth from your outstretched fingertips. Each creature in a 15-foot cone must make a Dexterity saving throw. A creature takes [[/r 3d6]] fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><p>The fire ignites any flammable objects in the area that aren't being worn or carried.</p><h3>At Higher Levels</h3><p>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the damage increases by [[/r 1d6]] for each slot level above 1st.</p><p><strong>Spell Lists.</strong> @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-journals.7iH4qANs2gxn0MIs.JournalEntryPage.NX28XQnco4pjOzF6]{Sorcerer}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-journals.7iH4qANs2gxn0MIs.JournalEntryPage.5YX3k6END6NQWHOB]{Wizard}</p>",
